      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-09-22/unite-billboard-campaign-urges-government-to-reverse-winter-fuel-allowance-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一家主要工会正在推出一系列广告牌，呼吁政府撤销有争议的冬季燃料补贴削减措施。]]></description>
