    <item>
      <title>以色列人担心西岸的袭击将引发更广泛的战争</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-22/israelis-fear-attack-from-restive-west-bank-will-spark-wider-war</link>
      <description><![CDATA[哈马斯袭击以色列南部、引发加沙战争并颠覆地区地缘政治格局已近一年，人们越来越担心巴勒斯坦武装分子可能从西岸发动类似入侵，引发更大范围的冲突。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-22/israelis-fear-attack-from-restive-west-bank-will-spark-wider-war</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 22 Sep 2024 07:30:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>金正恩在与俄罗斯交好的同时，对中国给予了温和的赞扬</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-22/kim-jong-un-offers-tepid-praise-to-china-as-he-cozies-up-to-russia</link>
      <description><![CDATA[朝鲜领导人金正恩以看似克制的言辞向中国国家主席习近平致以问候，而当前平壤正与俄罗斯走得更近，减少对其长期亚洲盟友的依赖。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-22/kim-jong-un-offers-tepid-praise-to-china-as-he-cozies-up-to-russia</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 22 Sep 2024 06:30:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
